    Democrats scramble to rein in Trump's Iran war powers
racing against the clock  shore up 
    Democrats are racing against the clock to shore up support for checking President Trump’s war powers as the fight shifts to the Senate.
第一句的定语从句  time frame  impeachment   trail
    Lawmakers looking to limit Trump’s ability to take military action against Iran face a tight time frame with little room for error after House Speaker Nancy Pelosi (D-Calif.) announced she will send the articles of impeachment to the Senate this week. 
    Once the trial begins, all legislation is expected to be delayed for weeks.
win over - 争取   call for - 要求
[amendment to] 
    The Senate previously voted 50-40 on an amendment to an annual defense policy bill that prevented Trump from using funding for military action against Iran. 
short of
    The measure fell short of the 60 votes needed for adoption.
pathway
    giving Kaine a pathway to 51 votes
closed-door briefing 句式
    Lee and Paul have said they will support Kaine’s war powers resolution after they left a closed-door briefing on the airstrike that killed Soleimani visibly angry with the administration.


















